<h3 class=3D"wp-block-heading" id=3D"h-final-thoughts">Final Thoughts</h3>



<p>While Stableford golf has been around for more than a century, it=E2=80=
=99s still one of the most fun ways to have fun on the golf course. It=E2=
=80=99s unfortunate that this different format isn=E2=80=99t used in the US=
 like it is in the UK (as it would definitely help with the pace of place i=
ssues the game is facing).</p>



<p>But if you can=E2=80=99t find a tournament or social outing that runs th=
is type of format, just create your own modified version with your buddies =
using an app mentioned in this post.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Not only will it break up the normal weekend routine but it will also <a=
 href=3D"https://theleftrough.com/pace-of-play/" target=3D"_blank" rel=3D"n=
oopener" data-lasso-id=3D"2388">speed up play</a> as well and reduce the nu=
mber of strokes taken. Since golfers can=E2=80=99t score worse than a doubl=
e bogey on each hole with this system, they can pick up <em>instead</em> of=
 letting a meltdown happen. This also makes it a great style for beginner p=
layers as well.</p><div id=3D"AdThrive_Content_10_tablet" class=3D"adthrive=
-ad adthrive-sticky-container adthrive-content adthrive-content-10 adthrive=
-ad-cls"></div>



<p>Finally, make sure that you clarify the point system <em>before</em> tee=
ing off if you=E2=80=99re using the modified version. This way, you and the=
 guys don=E2=80=99t have any post-round arguments in the 19th hole.&nbsp;</=
